{"lastModified":1764149106528,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::964e2090-ca12-11f0-8a0a-8325876a6634","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Aegean Sea, Greece\n\nEXPERIENCE THE EXCEPTIONAL\nS/CAT LORAIN, built in 2025 by Lagoon shipyard is perfect for exploring the Greek islands. She offers stability and seaworthiness while sailing, providing guests with a supreme cruising experience. Presenting a nice layout of 5 en-suite cabins, accommodating up to 10 guests, LORAIN is the ideal choice for a comfortable and luxurious sailing vacation.\n\nEnjoy the luxury of space, escape the everyday, and connect with nature. With its innovative layout, this catamaran offers durable solutions to preserve the environment and to protect your dream destinations. Explore the world aboard a Lagoon 51.\n\nAN INVITATION TO RELAX\nThis catamaran has been created for you to make long crossings in exceptional comfort. Relax on the flybridge, with its innovative, modular layout and clever ergonomic design, and enjoy the view: your dream of travel to far-off destinations is finally coming true.\n\nAN OCEAN OF PLEASURES\nThe silhouette of the Lagoon 51 reveals unique aft transoms, ensuring easy, safe movement on board. Together with the swim platform, this space becomes a true balcony on the water while cruising, and at anchor, an invitation to swim.","blueprint":{"name":"LORAIN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::964e2090-ca12-11f0-8a0a-8325876a6634::assets::9306f9f0-ca14-11f0-9f3e-654b27080079/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::964e2090-ca12-11f0-8a0a-8325876a6634::assets::93076f20-ca14-11f0-9f3f-654b27080079/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::964e2090-ca12-11f0-8a0a-8325876a6634::assets::930db0b0-ca14-11f0-a1c5-cf8faaffc6ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::964e2090-ca12-11f0-8a0a-8325876a6634::assets::9308f5c0-ca14-11f0-9f3f-654b27080079/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::964e2090-ca12-11f0-8a0a-83258